1

Firedamp Explosion 2 1 1 - 4

Firedamp Explosion allows Enutrofs to recover a Mine by moving it from the targeted cell to under the Enutrof. If the spell is cast on a target, that target will inflict damage on adjacent cells at the end of its turn.

Normal effects

Firedamp Explosion (+4 Lvl.)
If cast on a Mine:
- Moves the Mine onto the Enutrof's cell
- The Mine obeys the rules of Geology

Critical effects

Firedamp Explosion (+5 Lvl.)
If cast on a Mine:
- Moves the Mine onto the Enutrof's cell
- The Mine obeys the rules of Geology
